{"tid":1302503,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"阿媽唔會咗我表哥入HKU","createTime":"2019-07-10T03:26:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-10T03:57:53.000Z","uid":154406,"like":53,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"793b39452107f9158e1f3001bd6a61686d7a3c87","tid":1302503,"uid":154406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T03:26:41.000Z","msg":"是咁的 <br />\n<br />\n我表哥佢今年考dse，琴日放榜 <br />\n佢考得唔係太好，又怕呀媽擔心 <br />\n呀媽一生人既夢想佢佢個仔入大學 <br />\n因為佢d親戚街坊都無仔女入到U <br />\n<br />\n今日一早番左屋企時，呀媽係咁問佢成績點，夠唔夠分, 可以入邊間U <br />\n表哥心情唔好，是撚但但同呀媽佢佢去讀藥劑， <br />\n之後請入房訓較(尋晚通左頂) <br />\n<br />\n表哥起左身，屙完屎之後出黎 <br />\n發現成家人都好開心，呀爸呀媽叫撚晒佢d親戚姑嫂話今晚出黎食飯 <br />\n同個仔慶祝入到HKU讀藥劑 <br />\n<br />\n依個時候先知大撚獲 <br />\n表哥其實係去報IVE讀藥劑 <br />\n唔撚知邊個親戚街坊話係香港既大學，只有HKU有藥劑讀 <br />\n所以呀媽以為佢夠分入左HKU <br />\n<br />\n屌你 <br />\n我表哥頭先打電話比我 <br />\n問我點做好......... <br />\n<br />\n點算好"},{"pid":"1f460a3bec69b18282c6302cf392e46b4fb678b4","tid":1302503,"uid":154406,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T03:26:54.000Z","msg":"誤會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb3d86a199fe0cec9353abd63444b923f931e882","tid":1302503,"uid":154406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T03:30:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b11d54e5856adf846d096d3a09865df1444f82f8","tid":1302503,"uid":110298,"like":8,"dislike":3,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T03:31:10.000Z","msg":"仲未厭?"},{"pid":"c65b97e55e2847684952895744560956b11e3143","tid":1302503,"uid":154406,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"b11d54e5856adf846d096d3a09865df1444f82f8","tid":1302503,"uid":110298,"like":8,"dislike":3,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T03:31:10.000Z","msg":"仲未厭?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T03:31:34.000Z","msg":"真人真事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4cb765f444e5a1e6ab3c729372bb1dc763d9d8c","tid":1302503,"uid":226524,"like":7